messages.content:
以下は「ご飯処 晴れ風」(千葉県富里市の海鮮居酒屋)向けに作成した静的HTMLモックアップです。このデザイン・構成・文言を忠実に踏襲したNext.jsプロジェクトとして再構築してください。画像は全て「画像: ○○」というプレースホルダーのままにし、実写真の指定はしないでください。

--- 参考HTML ---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ご飯処 晴れ風 ｜ 富里・日吉台 名物"生鯖"と魚の店</title>
<meta name="description" content="千葉県富里市日吉台。名物の生鯖と旬の魚、日本酒50種を愉しむご飯処 晴れ風。ランチもディナーも営業する定食屋×居酒屋。">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Shippori+Mincho:wght@500;600;700;800&family=Zen+Kaku+Gothic+New:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --sumi:#181410;
  --sumi-soft:#241d16;
  --washi:#f2ebdd;
  --washi-dim:#e4dac5;
  --amber:#ef9740;
  --amber-deep:#d97e28;
  --seal:#b23b2e;
  --silver:#8fa2ad;
  --ink-70:rgba(242,235,221,.7);
  --ink-45:rgba(242,235,221,.45);
  --serif:"Shippori Mincho",serif;
  --gothic:"Zen Kaku Gothic New",sans-serif;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{
  background:var(--sumi);
  color:var(--washi);
  font-family:var(--gothic);
  font-weight:400;
  line-height:1.9;
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  overflow-x:hidden;
}
.wrap{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px}
a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
img{display:block;max-width:100%}

body::before{
  content:"";position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 82% -5%, rgba(239,151,64,.08), transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(900px 500px at -10% 100%, rgba(143,162,173,.05), transparent 60%);
}
main{position:relative;z-index:1}

.bar{
  position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;
  backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
  background:rgba(24,20,16,.75);
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(242,235,221,.08);
}
.bar .wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:64px}
.brand{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.18em;font-size:1.05rem}
.brand span{color:var(--amber)}
.nav{display:flex;gap:30px;font-size:.82rem;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--ink-70)}
.nav a{transition:color .25s}
.nav a:hover{color:var(--amber)}
.nav-cta{
  border:1px solid var(--amber);color:var(--amber);
  padding:7px 16px;border-radius:2px;font-size:.78rem;letter-spacing:.12em;
  transition:.25s;white-space:nowrap;
}
.nav-cta:hover{background:var(--amber);color:var(--sumi)}
@media(max-width:820px){.nav{display:none}}

.hero{
  min-height:92vh;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.15fr .85fr;
  align-items:center;gap:40px;padding:60px 0 80px;position:relative;
}
.hero-left{position:relative}
.eyebrow{
  font-family:var(--serif);color:var(--amber);letter-spacing:.36em;
  font-size:.78rem;margin-bottom:26px;
}
.hero h1{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:800;line-height:1.12;
  font-size:clamp(2.6rem,7vw,5.2rem);letter-spacing:.04em;
}
.hero h1 .sub{display:block;font-size:.32em;letter-spacing:.5em;color:var(--ink-70);margin-top:18px;font-weight:600}
.hero-lead{
  margin-top:32px;max-width:36ch;color:var(--ink-70);font-size:1.02rem;line-height:2.1;
}
.hero-lead b{color:var(--washi);font-weight:500}
.hero-meta{
  margin-top:38px;display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;
  font-size:.82rem;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--ink-70);
}
.rating{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;
  border:1px solid rgba(239,151,64,.4);border-radius:2px;padding:8px 14px;color:var(--washi)}
.rating b{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--amber);line-height:1}
.stars{color:var(--amber);letter-spacing:2px;font-size:.9rem}
.hero-actions{margin-top:36px;display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.btn{
  font-family:var(--gothic);font-size:.9rem;letter-spacing:.1em;
  padding:14px 26px;border-radius:2px;transition:.25s;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid transparent;
}
.btn-primary{background:var(--seal);color:var(--washi)}
.btn-primary:hover{background:#c9463a;transform:translateY(-2px)}
.btn-ghost{border-color:rgba(242,235,221,.25);color:var(--washi)}
.btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--amber);color:var(--amber)}

.noren{
  position:relative;height:520px;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:stretch;gap:18px;
}
.noren-panel{
  width:118px;border-radius:0 0 4px 4px;
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--amber),var(--amber-deep));
  box-shadow:0 30px 60px -30px rgba(0,0,0,.8);
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;padding-top:40px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.noren-panel::before{
  content:"";position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:12px;
  background:rgba(24,20,16,.85);
}
.tate{
  writing-mode:vertical-rl;text-orientation:upright;
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:800;font-size:2.6rem;letter-spacing:.22em;
  color:var(--sumi);
}
.noren-cap{
  writing-mode:vertical-rl;font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;
  font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:.3em;color:rgba(24,20,16,.7);margin-top:14px;
}
.noren-seal{
  position:absolute;right:-6px;bottom:44px;z-index:5;
  width:76px;height:76px;border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--seal);color:var(--washi);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:700;line-height:1.15;text-align:center;
  font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:.05em;
  box-shadow:0 10px 24px -8px rgba(178,59,46,.7);
  transform:rotate(-8deg);
}
.wind{position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;opacity:.35}
.wind path{stroke:var(--amber);stroke-width:1.4;fill:none;stroke-linecap:round}

@media(max-width:820px){
  .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:40px 0 60px}
  .noren{height:360px;order:-1;margin-bottom:10px}
  .noren-panel{width:86px}
  .tate{font-size:1.9rem}
}

.section{padding:96px 0;position:relative}
.section-head{margin-bottom:52px;display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.sec-no{font-family:var(--serif);color:var(--seal);font-size:1.1rem;letter-spacing:.2em}
.sec-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.6rem);letter-spacing:.08em}
.sec-en{color:var(--ink-45);font-size:.78rem;letter-spacing:.34em;align-self:center}

.menu-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:22px}
.dish{
  border:1px solid rgba(242,235,221,.1);border-radius:4px;padding:30px 30px 28px;
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(36,29,22,.7),rgba(30,24,18,.3));
  transition:.3s;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.dish:hover{border-color:rgba(239,151,64,.4);transform:translateY(-3px)}
.dish.feat{grid-column:1 / -1;display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto;gap:28px;align-items:center}
.dish .badge{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-size:.68rem;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--sumi);
  background:var(--amber);padding:4px 11px;border-radius:2px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:14px;
}
.dish h3{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:700;font-size:1.4rem;letter-spacing:.05em;line-height:1.4}
.dish .en{color:var(--ink-45);font-size:.74rem;letter-spacing:.16em;margin-top:6px}
.dish p{color:var(--ink-70);font-size:.92rem;margin-top:14px;line-height:1.95}
.dish .kanji-mark{
  writing-mode:vertical-rl;font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:800;
  font-size:2.4rem;color:var(--seal);letter-spacing:.1em;opacity:.9;
}
.price{font-family:var(--serif);color:var(--amber);font-size:1.05rem;white-space:nowrap;align-self:start;margin-top:4px}
.small-plates{
  margin-top:26px;border:1px solid rgba(242,235,221,.1);border-radius:4px;
  padding:26px 30px;background:rgba(36,29,22,.4);
}
.small-plates h4{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:6px;font-size:1.1rem}
.small-plates .en{color:var(--ink-45);font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:.16em;margin-bottom:18px}
.plate-list{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px}
.plate{
  font-size:.88rem;color:var(--ink-70);
  border:1px solid rgba(242,235,221,.16);padding:7px 15px;border-radius:2px;
}
@media(max-width:760px){
  .menu-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .dish.feat{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .dish .kanji-mark{writing-mode:horizontal-tb;font-size:1.8rem}
}

.sake{
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,#14100c,#181410);
  border-top:1px solid rgba(242,235,221,.08);
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(242,235,221,.08);
  text-align:center;
}
.sake .wrap{max-width:780px}
.sake .tate-quote{
  writing-mode:vertical-rl;font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:700;
  font-size:clamp(1.6rem,4vw,2.4rem);line-height:1.9;letter-spacing:.14em;
  height:300px;margin:0 auto;color:var(--washi);
}
.sake .tate-quote em{color:var(--amber);font-style:normal}
.sake p{color:var(--ink-70);margin-top:40px;font-size:.98rem}
.sake .sake-tags{margin-top:30px;display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.sake-tags .st{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-size:.82rem;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--amber);
  border:1px solid rgba(239,151,64,.4);padding:6px 16px;border-radius:2px;
}
@media(max-width:760px){.sake .tate-quote{height:auto;writing-mode:horizontal-tb}}

.voices{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}
.voice{
  border:1px solid rgba(242,235,221,.1);border-radius:4px;padding:28px 26px;
  background:rgba(36,29,22,.4);position:relative;
}
.voice .q{font-family:var(--serif);color:var(--seal);font-size:2.4rem;line-height:.6;opacity:.5}
.voice p{color:var(--washi);font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.95;margin:12px 0 20px}
.voice .who{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;font-size:.8rem;color:var(--ink-70)}
.avatar{
  width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--amber),var(--seal));
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:700;color:var(--sumi);font-size:.8rem;
}
.who .stars{color:var(--amber);font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:1px}
@media(max-width:900px){.voices{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

.info-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;gap:48px;align-items:start}
.info-list{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}
.info-list th,.info-list td{
  text-align:left;padding:18px 4px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(242,235,221,.1);
  vertical-align:top;font-size:.95rem;
}
.info-list th{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;color:var(--amber);
  letter-spacing:.12em;width:120px;white-space:nowrap;
}
.info-list td{color:var(--ink-70)}
.info-list td b{color:var(--washi);font-weight:500}
.info-list a{color:var(--washi);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(239,151,64,.4);transition:.2s}
.info-list a:hover{color:var(--amber)}
.hours-card{
  border:1px solid rgba(239,151,64,.3);border-radius:4px;padding:32px 30px;
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(239,151,64,.06),transparent);
}
.hours-card h4{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;margin-bottom:20px}
.hours-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px dashed rgba(242,235,221,.14)}
.hours-row .label{font-family:var(--serif);color:var(--amber);letter-spacing:.1em;font-size:.92rem}
.hours-row .time{font-size:1.05rem;letter-spacing:.04em}
.tags{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:24px}
.tag{
  font-size:.72rem;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--ink-70);
  border:1px solid rgba(242,235,221,.18);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px;
}
.radio{
  margin-top:26px;border-left:2px solid var(--seal);padding:6px 0 6px 18px;
  font-size:.86rem;color:var(--ink-70);line-height:1.85;
}
.radio b{color:var(--washi);font-family:var(--serif)}
@media(max-width:760px){.info-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:32px}}

footer{
  padding:64px 0 48px;text-align:center;
  border-top:1px solid rgba(242,235,221,.08);
}
.foot-brand{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:800;font-size:1.8rem;letter-spacing:.2em}
.foot-brand span{color:var(--amber)}
.foot-lead{color:var(--ink-45);font-size:.82rem;letter-spacing:.14em;margin-top:14px}
.foot-links{display:flex;gap:26px;justify-content:center;margin-top:28px;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--ink-70);flex-wrap:wrap}
.foot-links a:hover{color:var(--amber)}
.copyright{margin-top:36px;font-size:.72rem;color:var(--ink-45);letter-spacing:.1em}

.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease}
.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}
@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){
  .reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}
  html{scroll-behavior:auto}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="bar">
  <div class="wrap">
    <a class="brand" href="#top">晴れ<span>風</span></a>
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="#menu">品書き</a>
      <a href="#sake">日本酒</a>
      <a href="#voices">お客様の声</a>
      <a href="#info">店舗案内</a>
    </nav>
    <a class="nav-cta" href="tel:09054462391">ご予約 090-5446-2391</a>
  </div>
</header>

<main id="top">

  <section class="wrap hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <p class="eyebrow reveal">千葉県富里市 日吉台 ・ 定食屋 × 居酒屋</p>
      <h1 class="reveal">ご飯処<br>晴れ風
        <span class="sub">H A R E K A Z E</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-lead reveal">名物は<b>"生鯖"</b>。鮮度が命の魚を、いちばん旨い切り方で。取り揃えた<b>日本酒は50種</b>。昼は出汁の効いた定食、夜は刺盛りに一献。若い二人が営む、日吉台のご飯処です。</p>

      <div class="hero-meta reveal">
        <span class="rating"><b>4.9</b><span class="stars">★★★★★</span></span>
        <span>Googleクチコミ 96件</span>
        <span>・</span>
        <span>お一人 ¥1,000〜2,000</span>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-actions reveal">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:09054462391">電話で予約する</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#menu">品書きを見る</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-right reveal">
      <div class="noren">
        <svg class="wind" viewBox="0 0 300 520" preserveAspectRatio="none">
          <path d="M10 60 q60 -20 120 0 t150 0"/>
          <path d="M0 120 q70 -22 140 0 t150 0"/>
          <path d="M20 470 q60 20 120 0 t150 0"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="noren-panel"><span class="tate">晴</span></div>
        <div class="noren-panel"><span class="tate">れ</span></div>
        <div class="noren-panel"><span class="tate">風</span><span class="noren-cap">ご飯処</span></div>
        <div class="noren-seal">生鯖<br>と魚</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="menu">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="sec-no">壱</span>
        <h2 class="sec-title">品書き</h2>
        <span class="sec-en">SIGNATURE DISHES</span>
      </div>

      <div class="menu-grid">
        <div class="dish feat reveal">
          <span class="kanji-mark">鯖</span>
          <div>
            <span class="badge">名物</span>
            <h3>むじょか 生鯖刺身定食</h3>
            <div class="en">MUJOKA RAW MACKEREL SET</div>
            <p>鮮度が命の生の鯖を、厚めに引いた刺身で。噛むほどに脂の甘みが広がる看板の一皿を、炊きたてのご飯と自家製の味噌汁で。晴れ風といえば、まずこれを。</p>
          </div>
          <span class="price">定食 ¥1,500〜</span>
        </div>

        <div class="dish reveal">
          <span class="badge">人気</span>
          <h3>晴れ式<br>鶏の唐揚げ定食</h3>
          <div class="en">HARE-STYLE KARAAGE SET</div>
          <p>下味からこだわった、外は香ばしく中はジューシーな唐揚げ。ランチの定番として長く愛される、間違いのない一皿です。</p>
          <span class="price">定食 ¥1,200〜</span>
        </div>

        <div class="dish reveal">
          <h3>刺盛り<br>盛り合わせ</h3>
          <div class="en">SASHIMI ASSORTMENT</div>
          <p>その日の仕入れから旬の魚を。真鯛のお刺身をはじめ、一切れが分厚く、日本酒を合わせずにはいられない贅沢な盛り合わせです。</p>
          <span class="price">時価</span>
        </div>

        <div class="dish reveal">
          <h3>和牛カレー</h3>
          <div class="en">WAGYU CURRY</div>
          <p>和牛の旨みをじっくり溶け込ませた、居酒屋の一品とは思えない本格カレー。ランチにも昼飲みの〆にも人気です。</p>
          <span class="price">¥1,200</span>
        </div>

        <div class="dish reveal">
          <h3>太刀魚と<br>大葉チーズフライ</h3>
          <div class="en">TACHIUO &amp; SHISO CHEESE FRY</div>
          <p>旬の太刀魚に大葉とチーズを巻いて揚げた、当店らしい一品。おすすめ黒板に並ぶ、日替わりの逸品からひとつ。</p>
          <span class="price">おすすめ</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="small-plates reveal">
        <h4>一品料理・本日のおすすめ</h4>
        <div class="en">SMALL PLATES &amp; WEEKLY SPECIALS</div>
        <div class="plate-list">
          <span class="plate">アサリチャンジャ</span>
          <span class="plate">きんぴらごぼう</span>
          <span class="plate">インゲンのマヨ味噌ディップ</span>
          <span class="plate">真鯛のお刺身</span>
          <span class="plate">まぐろと大根の煮込み</span>
          <span class="plate">里芋の煮ころがし</span>
          <span class="plate">ヤングコーンと生ハムチーズの春巻</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section sake" id="sake">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="tate-quote reveal">旬を肴に、<br><em>一献かたむける。</em></div>
      <p class="reveal">全国から選りすぐった<b style="color:var(--washi)">日本酒50種</b>。三重の「作（ざく）」、高知、栃木の地酒まで、刺身と定食に寄り添う一杯を日替わりで。昼飲みも、仕事帰りの一杯も、家族のごはんも。晴れ風は、そんな時間のための店です。</p>
      <div class="sake-tags reveal">
        <span class="st">日本酒 50種</span>
        <span class="st">作 -三重-</span>
        <span class="st">昼飲み歓迎</span>
        <span class="st">全国の地酒</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="voices">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="sec-no">弐</span>
        <h2 class="sec-title">お客様の声</h2>
        <span class="sec-en">FROM OUR GUESTS</span>
      </div>

      <div class="voices">
        <div class="voice reveal">
          <div class="q">&ldquo;</div>
          <p>落ち着いた店内で、ゆっくり食事を楽しめました。丁寧で温かみのある接客が印象に残っています。</p>
          <div class="who">
            <span class="avatar">I</span>
            <div>I.D. さん<br><span class="stars">★★★★★ ・ ローカルガイド</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

